data.description: Nestled in a cozy neighborhood, this 4-bedroom, 3-bath abode offers the perfect blend of comfortable living and southern charm. The updated kitchen featuring stainless steel, granite countertops, and ample cabinetry. Whip up your favorite meals and make memories that last a lifetime!  The primary suite with private deck offers a peaceful retreat to end your busy days, while the additional bedrooms provide plenty of space for everyone. Get ready to host the best backyard BBQs in your huge, fenced-in yard. Did we mention the deck? A brand-new deck will be completed by October 25th, offering the perfect spot to sip your morning coffee or unwind with an evening cocktail.  The full finished basement comes complete with a bedroom and a full bath, making it a versatile space for whatever your heart desires. Cherryville is more than just a place to live; it's a community where neighbors know your name. Conveniently located, you're just a quick drive away from shops, restaurants, and parks.
